data.description: Beautiful one-level living with a backyard oasis!  This split bedroom floorplan offers a large greatroom and recently updated kitchen with hand scraped wood floors and new carpet.  Other features inside include gorgeous trim, fresh paint, walk-in closets and updated bathrooms.  All of this on almost a half acre lot, fenced backyard, above ground pool with deck, hot tub, and storage building!  Conveniently located minutes from College Grove and 840!
